Subject: [PATCH 2/2] virglrenderer: extend contexts to map OPAQUE_HANDLE

Renderer contexts can optionally implement resource_map() to map
OPAQUE_HANDLE blobs on behalf of the VMM. This is specially useful for
native context implementations as allows them to honor BO sharing
semantics.

Co-authored-by: Pierre-Eric Pelloux-Prayer <pierre-eric.pelloux-prayer@amd.com>
Co-authored-by: Dmitry Osipenko <dmitry.osipenko@collabora.com>
Signed-off-by: Sergio Lopez <slp@sinrega.org>
Part-of: <https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/virgl/virglrenderer/-/merge_requests/1374>
